exceptions.exn: Cannot coerce L to an evaluable reference.
Expects a disjunctive pattern with 0 branches.

original: intros m x H1 H2. unfold nf. unfold L. unfold B. simpl. destruct H1 as [_ H1]. destruct H2 as [H2 _]. destruct (eq_dim_dec zero zero) as [H3 | H3]. - destruct (eq_dart_dec x x) as [H4 | H4]. + reflexivity. + contradict H4. reflexivity. - contradict H3. reflexivity.
